title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 26 2022
description:
New York Post columnist Miranda Devine joins Clay and Buck to discuss Elon Musk’s Twitter takeover and the latest on Hunter Biden and the Laptop from Hell (also the name of her book about him). The highest-paid face of ESPN, Stephen A. Smith, goes after NBA player Ben Simmons for acting like Simone Biles. Author Douglas Murray, associate editor of The Spectator, joins C&B to talk about his new book, The War on the West, and what we can do to push back on liberal attacks on our history. The Regime's not interested in where covid came from.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
